features: ADVENTUROUS SPIRIT: Embrace the outdoors with Bear Grylls Mosquito Repellent Bracelets - designed to keep you protected in the wild without compromising on safety or style.

DEET-FREE DEFENCE: Bear Grylls Mosquito Repellent Bracelets offer effective mosquito protection using only naturally-derived essential oils. No DEET here! Dermatologically tested and safe for even sensitive skin, each bracelet emits a pleasant, insect-repelling aroma suitable for every explorer.
LONG-LASTING PROTECTION: Stay protected from mosquitoes and ticks for up to 10 hours per bracelet. Pair with Bear Grylls Mosquito Repellent spray for an even more comprehensive bite protection.
ADJUSTABLE AND COLOURFUL: Bear Grylls Mosquito Repellent Bracelets are adjustable to fit any wrist or ankle, and come in a variety of bold colours, combining style with reliable protection.
FAMILY FRIENDLY: Suitable for children aged 6 months and above, Bear Grylls Mosquito Repellent Bracelets provide a safe and effective insect repellent option for the whole family.
